      "date": "2012-04-06 07:41:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nRebase against the latest master branch.\n\nUp layer LFSCK does not depends on some special returned values from low layer dt iteration APIs. It does three things:\n\n1) Scan the specified device by dt iteration APIs.\n\n2) Feed the LFSCK components in its layer with the scanned objects.\n\n3) Speed control for the whole LFSCK.",
